Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.54,0:00:02.22,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,This brand new school of friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.60,0:00:04.22,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Is home to everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.60,0:00:06.22,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We're learning how to trust
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.60,0:00:08.47,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We're here to all have fun
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.66,0:00:12.22,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,With friendship ties that bind us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.97,0:00:15.97,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Tighter than~ the strongest bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.85,0:00:19.72,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We're hoof-in-hoof~~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.35,0:00:25.79,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,In hand in hoof in wing or even claw
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:34.78,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,There's a griffon in the garden
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.10,0:00:36.85,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Hippogriffs hang in the hall
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:38.78,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And the door will be open to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.91,0:00:40.85,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,All creatures great and small
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.16,0:00:42.72,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And a yak or two or three
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.03,0:00:44.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Sing in perfect harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.85,0:00:46.60,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That might have been a changeling
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.78,0:00:50.35,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But it kind of looks like me~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.35,0:00:54.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,This school of friendship is for all of us~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.91,0:00:56.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A place where we belong~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.91,0:00:59.10,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Where we all learn to share and trust
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.53,0:01:02.78,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The only rule here is to find your way~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.03,0:01:07.47,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And friendship always wins at the end~ of the day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.78,0:01:18.91,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Some things you just can't teach with books
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:22.60,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Some things you only know~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.91,0:01:26.97,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,So trust your heart and let us lead~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.22,0:01:31.03,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And your friendship's~ sure to grow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.03,0:01:34.91,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And once we master kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.35,0:01:39.16,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,We will spread it 'cross this land
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.72,0:01:43.28,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And give the gift that's ours to share
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.53,0:01:48.03,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,So others understand
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:51.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,This school of friendship is for all of us~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.91,0:01:53.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A place where we belong~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.91,0:01:56.03,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Where we all learn to share and trust
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.47,0:01:59.78,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The only rule here is to find your way~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.03,0:02:04.41,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And friendship always wins at the end~ of the day